    "body": "## What's Changed\r\n* refs #95: implemented websocket support; by @bogdanfinn in https://github.com/bogdanfinn/tls-client/pull/208\r\n* Update contributed_browser_profiles.go - Add Firefox 146, 147 by @gunir in https://github.com/bogdanfinn/tls-client/pull/209\r\n* Add EUC-KR encoding for Korean by @ahnse0 in https://github.com/bogdanfinn/tls-client/pull/207\r\n* feat: HTTP/3 fingerprinting for Chrome 144 and Firefox 147 by @bogdanfinn in https://github.com/bogdanfinn/tls-client/pull/215\r\n* Add Safari iOS 26.0, Chrome 146, Chrome 146 PSK, tests by @nihiloid in https://github.com/bogdanfinn/tls-client/pull/214\r\n* [Bug]: ipv6 url error by @zephyr-profile in https://github.com/bogdanfinn/tls-client/pull/212\r\n* fixed websocket connection; by @bogdanfinn in https://github.com/bogdanfinn/tls-client/pull/216\r\n* print detected pins in error message in case of \"bad ssl pin detected\" by @AndreaVitale in https://github.com/bogdanfinn/tls-client/pull/217\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @ahnse0 made their first contribution in https://github.com/bogdanfinn/tls-client/pull/207\r\n* @zephyr-profile made their first contribution in https://github.com/bogdanfinn/tls-client/pull/212\r\n* @AndreaVitale made their first contribution in https://github.com/bogdanfinn/tls-client/pull/217\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/bogdanfinn/tls-client/compare/v1.13.1...v1.14.0",
